node.text: #WCOxTaraMilkTea ✨ Created for the wanderlust dreamers, it felt so special to be wearing my collection pieces for our final trip of the year (and the decade) in one of the most beautiful places on earth. These pieces mean so much to me and have been all around the world for the last half year, and I’m excited to wear them well into the new decade. @wanderlustandco ✨

node.text: Styling my bedroom with @Koala! 🛌 🐨 I've been sleeping on a Koala mattress for over three years, and always miss it when I'm travelling! We recently got their bed base which was way too easy to set up, and I love it's minimal look! We also use their sheets which are sooo soft, making coming home so cosy, especially after a long day of flying! Use MATESWITHTMT for 10% off everything #sleepwithkoala #ad

Made it to Paris with @huaweimobileau for the launch of their new P30 & P30 pro! The camera has insane capabilities, this was shot on the new P30 pro using the wide lens function on the camera! #HuaweiP30Pro #RewriteTheRules #sponsored

node.text:
The excitement is real. She’s getting ready to travel in 2022!

I am partnering with @cdcgov to share why I’m vaccinated for COVID-19. I feel so privileged to have been able to be vaccinated, I put my trust in the health care professionals to keep me safe. Having lived my life on the road for the past few years life lately has felt a little paused. I’m incredibly grateful for my home, but I can’t wait to be in the skies again and I have felt safer living life vaccinated! Here are some of my favourite NYC memories from the holiday season … See you in the skies next year! ☁️ 

If you are thinking about getting vaccinated, click the link in my stories to learn more at vaccines.gov⁠
#TravelVaxxed
